html { margin:0; padding:0; font-size:62.5%; }
body { max-width:800px; min-width:300px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px 10px; font-size:14px; font-size:1.4em; }
h1 { font-size:1.8em; }

/* Styles for wrapping the search box */

.search {
    position: absolute;
    width: 25%;
    right: 10px;
}

/* Bootstrap 3 text input with search icon */

.has-search .form-control-feedback {
    right: initial;
    left: 0;
    color: #ccc;
}

.has-search .form-control {
    padding-right: 12px;
    padding-left: 34px;
}

/* The Modal (background) */
.modal {
    display: none; /* Hidden by default */
    position: fixed; /* Stay in place */
    z-index: 1; /* Sit on top */
    padding-top: 100px; /* Location of the box */
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%; /* Full width */
    height: 100%; /* Full height */
    overflow: auto; /* Enable scroll if needed */
    background-color: rgb(0,0,0); /* Fallback color */
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); /* Black w/ opacity */
    font-size:1.2em;
}

/* Modal Content */
.modal-content {
    background-color: #fefefe;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #888;
    width: 80%;
}

/* The Close Button */
.close {
    color: #aaaaaa;
    float: right;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.close:hover,
.close:focus {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.scrollable {
    max-height: 340px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    overflow-y: auto;
}

@font-face{
    font-family: "Glyphicons Halflings";
    src: url(data:application/x-font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("woff2"),
    url(data:application/x-font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("woff"),
    url(data:application/x-font-ttf;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("truetype");
}
